{"tid":2014633,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"高速公路內線開93公里時速收告票 台灣高速公路警察局 : 因為開太慢","createTime":"2020-05-13T06:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T15:07:32.000Z","uid":253829,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"2d13fc9fbef963bba3e299dd96446420491ae405","tid":2014633,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"一名駕駛BMW轎車的葉姓男子，日前駕車行經國道1號時，僅以93公里時速行駛在內側車道上，後來收到「未依最低速限行駛」罰單，氣得上臉書爆料公社討拍直呼「以為我開法拉利加速很快哦？我開車30年沒聽過這法規啊！」但貼文沒多久就被網友們高速打臉尷尬刪文；而高速公路警察局粉專也忍不住現身開嘲諷「98已經忍了，93又來爆，慢速車不佔用內車道都宣導很久了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hrPXt_H0ALX9lDQWtNdNSKF9bLhBWYT58ATt8fCZjc0scbm4tDGJqEUZadUtJOmohCz5hEUAMNk4bamogXG1q/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hrPXt_H0ALX9lDQWtNdNSKF9bLhBWYT58ATt8fCZjc0scbm4tDGJqEUZadUtJOmohCz5hEUAMNk4bamogXG1q%2Fw644&h=884d06e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲葉男在爆料公社貼文討拍。（圖／翻攝自爆料公社）<br />\n<br />\n這名葉姓男子日前在臉書爆料公社上貼文指出「請問一下各位，我那天在一高，為了超越前面這台慢車而切進內側車道，卻看見路邊的雷射槍，也就沒有加速，那時車速在93。結果上面他媽的寫三小【未依最低速限行駛】？速限也就90啊！你內側車道我要快也不行啊！剛超車你以為我開法拉利加速很快哦？自己看照片距離，你想賺業績不是用這種猥瑣的方式吧？還是其實內側車道不能低於110？我開車30年沒聽過這法規啊！還請各位幫我解釋一下，這可以去舉報吧」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hDYsbWZT9G3ZOGzOkHsZkIXRNGBl9dwh1Ki1KdQ11RUI3eFgkJ3QEGG0fFhY0eVwoIChXGG4ZAEcwfFwpd3sE/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hDYsbWZT9G3ZOGzOkHsZkIXRNGBl9dwh1Ki1KdQ11RUI3eFgkJ3QEGG0fFhY0eVwoIChXGG4ZAEcwfFwpd3sE%2Fw644&h=a158beb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲葉男在爆料公社貼文討拍。（圖／翻攝自爆料公社）<br />\n<br />\n由於日前才有一個女車主在內側車道開98公里遭開單的討拍貼文，因此網友看到葉男貼文後，以「光速」打臉，紛紛痛批「害大家堵車30年了，第31年終於有人好好教育他了。龜車請開外線車道」、「開了30年的路隊長」、「看了心情真好」、「欠教育的駕駛真不少, 違法30年, 被抓到一次就該該叫」、「台灣駕照真的太好換了，一支雞腿就能換到了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hVen306D5CUpTSiGYA412HWkcCiVgJhpJN3xYSRAkV34qKUoYOiRHJHBPXih_ck4UPXlELHZJEnstLU4VaiVH/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hVen306D5CUpTSiGYA412HWkcCiVgJhpJN3xYSRAkV34qKUoYOiRHJHBPXih_ck4UPXlELHZJEnstLU4VaiVH%2Fw644&h=94620291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲葉男在爆料公社貼文討拍。（圖／翻攝自爆料公社）<br />\n<br />\n國道公路警察局小編也忍不住開嘲諷表示「你看看就說有在取締，結果一直被爆料，98已經忍了 93又來爆，等等會不會95也來了，人客啊，來評評理，慢速車不佔用內車道都宣導很久了，小編心好累（怒摔筆），看來不靠鄉民的力量不行」最後更表示「慢速車請勿佔用內車道、沒聽過不代表可以違規」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hpUe3-_m6L3pYSgeoCI1QLWIcLBVrJjx5PHx-eRskcU4hKWwoMSRhFHtDd0tyeGgkNnliHHxMNEsmLWglYSVh/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hpUe3-_m6L3pYSgeoCI1QLWIcLBVrJjx5PHx-eRskcU4hKWwoMSRhFHtDd0tyeGgkNnliHHxMNEsmLWglYSVh%2Fw644&h=f4a217bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b9d732241625750cbff6fb1f330a57cfc51d774","tid":2014633,"uid":66365,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:59:47.000Z","msg":"寶馬撚根本係馬路炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af2c3824ae15aae2c31a07cbee8feee69925246","tid":2014633,"uid":810,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:38:02.000Z","msg":"即係快線撚?"},{"pid":"afa5bb65ce4473031c71be8053b345052afe5bfd","tid":2014633,"uid":66242,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzfTRuy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgzfTRuy.png&h=fa5abe97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7ff6b5d9442a4b99cbca757b815d34660e28c61","tid":2014633,"uid":66242,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://a.udn.com/focus/2015/10/20/13512/image/chart01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa.udn.com%2Ffocus%2F2015%2F10%2F20%2F13512%2Fimage%2Fchart01.jpg&h=d3b61d04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce9cf2a7cecb8bf5a4bf04e8cc71c1daf8f4f3b9","tid":2014633,"uid":66242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://tw.iscarmg.com/images/News/Taiwan/Tony/20160223/lows